Class Project

java.lang.Object
com.SC2002.bto.entities.Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a BTO (Build-To-Order) housing project. This class encapsulates all the details of a housing project including project information, flat types, pricing, application dates, and management details.

  • Constructor Details

    • Project

      public Project(int projectId, String projectName, String neighborhood, String type1Desc, int type1Units, int type1Price, String type2Desc, int type2Units, int type2Price, LocalDate applicationOpeningDate, LocalDate applicationClosingDate, String manager, int officerSlots, List<String> officers)
      Constructs a new Project with all required details.
      Parameters:
      projectId - Unique identifier for the project
      projectName - Name of the BTO project
      neighborhood - Neighborhood/location of the project
      type1Desc - Description of the first flat type
      type1Units - Number of available units for the first flat type
      type1Price - Price of the first flat type in SGD
      type2Desc - Description of the second flat type
      type2Units - Number of available units for the second flat type
      type2Price - Price of the second flat type in SGD
      applicationOpeningDate - Date when applications for this project open
      applicationClosingDate - Date when applications for this project close
      manager - NRIC of the HDB manager responsible for this project
      officerSlots - Number of HDB officer positions available for this project
      officers - List of HDB officers (by NRIC) assigned to this project
